Prism is an application that lets users split web applications 
out of their browser and run them directly on their desktop

http://prism.mozillalabs.com/
Prism is a Mozilla Labs http://labs.mozilla.com/about-labs/ project.

This is a generic installer for Prism.  As-is, it is only marginally useful. 
Instead, use this as a base for more detailed installations.

Installation system:  http://nsis.sourceforge.net/

Questions/Comments:  Email me at drmikecrowe (at) gmail (dot) com


